Easy trains with unloading stations and many loading stations (1:n relation). Compatible with City Plots blueprint and no need of mods or complicated circuit logic.

# How to use it

Copy the code here, import the blueprint book in the game and use the blueprints.

```txt

```

The only important thing to pay attention is the unloading stations needs unique symbols for the "Unique Symbol" parameter! I use the number symbols, but the letter symbols would also work. I will change that to be able to scale better if I need lot more unloading stations:

The only blueprint I dont done on my own, I used another one and changed it to fit into a city plot. Its highly optimized for throughput and I also use it if I only need a 3-Way junction.

![](4-way-throughput.png)

## Unloading Solid

Unloading station for solid ressource including the supported amount of trains:
* Trains already have the stops to load and unload the ressource and an interrupt to refuel if needed
* Gripping arms are filtered for the ressource to prevent unloading accidentally other ressources if drive other trains manually to the station
* Cargo waggons are limited to the ressource to prevent loading other ressources if driven manually
* Outgoing lines are balanced by 8x8 balancer

![](unloading-solid.png)

## Unloading Liquid

Unloading station for liquid ressource including the supported amount of trains:
* Trains already have the stops to load and unload the ressource and an interrupt to refuel if needed
* Pumps are filtered for the ressource to prevent unloading accidentally other ressources if drive other trains manually to the station

![](unloading-liquid.png)

## Loading Solid

Loading station for solid ressource:
* Not locked to a city plot, can freely attached to a straight track
* Limit the trains drive to the station to the amount of trains which can be fully loaded by small curciut logic
* Gripping arms are filtered for the ressource to prevent storing and loading accidentally other ressources
* Incoming lines are balanced by 8x8 balancer

![](loading-solid.png)

## Loading Liquid

Loading station for liquid ressource:
* Not locked to a city plot, can freely attached to a straight track

* Pumps are filtered for the ressource to prevent storing and loading accidentally other ressources
